      <item>
        <title>Messages</title>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;messages&quot;&gt;Messages&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-error&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-remove-sign&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Oops, something wrong happened.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-help&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-help-sign&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Do you need any help?&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-info&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-info-sign&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Here&#39;s more information.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-warn&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-warning-sign&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Warning! something might be wrong.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-ok&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-ok-sign&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Everything is great!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ch-box-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-truck&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Generic message, with an icon.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;how-to-use&quot;&gt;How to use&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add class &lt;strong&gt;ch-box-icon&lt;/strong&gt; to any block element (div, section, p, etc.). Combine with any class listed below to give contextual styling (&lt;a href=&quot;#boxes&quot;&gt;see Boxes&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;ch-list&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-lite&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-container&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-error&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-help&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-info&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-warn&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;ch-box-ok&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add &lt;a href=&quot;#icons&quot;&gt;any icon&lt;/a&gt; into any box for more contextual messages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;
&lt;code class=&quot;language-markup&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div class=&quot;ch-box-icon ch-box-error&quot;&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;i class=&quot;ch-icon-remove-sign&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt; Oops, something wrong happened.
&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
</description>
